notam.notam:
CYMX WEF 2018 AUG 16 1200 AMEND PUB: PRO: ADD:
THE MINISTER HAS AUTH SPECIFIC OPR RESTRICTIONS REGARDING COM
INTENDED FOR THE MF, AS WELL AS THE INTRODUCTION OF A GROUND
ADVISORY FREQ (GND ADV) PURSUANT TO CAR 602.97 (2), 602.98 (1)
AND 602.99.
DEP PROC: TO READ: PRIOR TO TAXI FOR DEP: CTC GND ADV ON 121.8
FOR CLR AND INITIAL ADVISORY INFO. AFTER RECEIVING INITIAL
ADVISORY INFO, GND ADV WILL INITIATE COM TRANSFER TO RDO 119.1
PRIOR TO ENTERING THE RUNWAY/DEP SURFACE.
PILOTS ARE REQUIRED TO ASCERTAIN THAT THERE IS NO LIKELIHOOD OF
COLLISION WITH ANOTHER ACFT OR A VEHICLE PRIOR TO DEP. (AS
STATED IN CAR 602.96, 2A AND B)
ADD: ARR PROC: AFTER EXITING THE RWY/ARR SURFACE AND REPORTING
CLEAR ON THE RDO FREQ, PILOTS WILL BE DIRECTED TO CTC GND ADV
ON 121.8 FOR GROUND TFC AND TAXIING INFO BFR ENTERING THE TWY.
